title: Dread knigth garen unoptainable
body: I am a EUW player and when i put the dread knigth garen skin it create an error please help me

replies.body: I went to see if I could get that skin added for ya, but it actually looks like there's something weird going on with your account on the backend preventing this from working. Hit up the EUW agents in a [**ticket**](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new) so they can take a look and get this fixed!
